reviews.customers_say: Customers find the sweater soft and comfortable, with one noting it retains quality after washing. They appreciate its cute design, with one highlighting the cool pattern in the front, and consider it well worth the money for its amazing quality. The material receives positive feedback, and customers find it warm, with one mentioning it's great for winter wear. Opinions about the size are mixed.

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Cute and Comfortable
items.body: Great quality heavy sweater. Very cozy and comfortable. Large and oversized, which is what I wanted so that's not a complaint. Received as a gift from my husband for anime nights and I get a lot of compliments on it when I wear it out. Definitely a great gift for anyone that's a fan of Death Note. Read more
items.author: ChesNoLastName

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars So cute and soft
items.body: I bought this for my daughter’s 16th birthday. After some research, I found that this is from the anime Death Note. I noticed she owned a death note t shirt and this sweater seems to be her style so I ordered this for her. I am so pleased with the fabric. It is much softer than expected. I got her the medium. It seems true to size. It will be a little oversized on her which I think will be perfect. I know she is going to love this. The price for the quality and the uniqueness of the sweater is on point! Read more

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars LOVE IT
items.body: The media could not be loaded. I’m literally in love with this sweater I definitely recommend it. I’m 5’1” and around 114 lbs and it fits oversized on me in the size medium (which is what I wanted). It’s super soft and warm plus it looks like it does in the pictures. I haven’t had any issues with it and I’ve had it for a while, definitely worth the money. Read more

items.title: 5.0 out of 5 stars Misa and L
items.body: I was afraid it would be low quality but it’s pretty and comfy I’m in love Read more
items.author: mati

items.title: 4.0 out of 5 stars Soft; good quality; weird smell
items.body: 5'6 112lbs, ordered size medium. Came in early, packaging not damaged, as assumed. Okay I absolutely ADORE this sweater, love, love, love it. Make sure to get a size up for the more oversized look, I have broad shoulders so I should've ordered a large!! But, it was an unexpected material, not a problem, it was very, very soft, stretchy, and durable. Came in folded tightly, so make sure to press wrinkles out (personally just wearing it for a bit got rid of them.) It also came with a really weird smell, it was chemically but different? I don't really know how to describe it. Other than that, it is basically perfect! For the price it was okay, but I'm definitely happy with this purchase. 100% recommend if you're not on a budget. Read more

items.body: I was concerned that I would be very thin but the material is quite soft and thick. Very breathable and I didn't notice any color smudging during the first few washes. Overall great purchase! Read more

short_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is made for a polished look that still feels comfortable to wear. It is designed to sit cleanly on the body with a flattering shape that works for day plans and dressier moments without feeling overdone.

The fit focuses on balance rather than extremes, so you can move naturally while still getting a defined silhouette. Choose your usual size for a closer look, or size up if you prefer a little more ease through the waist and hips.

Styling is simple: keep accessories minimal for a clean finish, or add a jacket and statement shoes when you want a sharper outfit. This piece photographs well thanks to smooth lines and a structured feel that stays put once you have it adjusted.

With the right fit and simple styling, this item becomes an easy go-to when you want something that looks intentional without requiring extra effort.

This piece transitions well from daytime plans to evening events with a quick change of shoes and a small bag or clutch.

long_description:
Womens Maxi Dress Long Sleeve is a versatile piece you can reach for when you want a put-together look that still feels comfortable. The goal is simple: a silhouette that reads polished, photographs well, and stays wearable for a full day or a long night.

Fit and sizing Fit is where most outfits win or lose. This design aims for a balanced shape with a defined line through the torso, a clean waist, and a smooth finish through the hips and legs. If you prefer a more relaxed feel, size up; if you like a closer fit, stay true to size. Sizes may include: XS, S, M, L, XL.

Fabric and comfort Comfort is not just about softness. It is also about movement and how the fabric behaves as you walk, sit, and stand. A fabric blend with a bit of give helps it keep its shape while still feeling wearable.

Highlights A clean neckline and a refined silhouette for an elevated look. Designed to layer easily with jackets, wraps, or sweaters. Works well with both minimal accessories and statement pieces.

How to style Styling ideas: keep it minimal with neutral shoes and one standout accessory. For a relaxed daytime look, add a denim jacket or cardigan. For events, switch to a bolder shoe and a small clutch for a sharper finish.

Color notes Available colors may include: Black. If a shade is sold out, check back as availability can change.

Care Care guidance matters if you want it to keep its shape and finish. Follow the label first.
